se350.elevatorSim.person

Class PersonResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • se350.elevatorSim.person.PersonResults
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<PersonResults>

    public class PersonResults
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<PersonResults>
    Simple Data Transfer Object that helps a user send their completed report of waiting and ride times to the Report Generator. The data is already checked for errors before this, so no error checking is necessary, therefore all data members are public.
    Author:
    James R Hagle
